rComments: Easy going, very approachable and always seeking ways to improve student uni life.
Amazing prof. Will do anything to help students with school or finding a job. Very passionate about subject matter. Loves to joke around with students. Sad to hear she's leaving for the US!
It is clear that she is passionate about the subject matter.  I look forward to the lectures.  Once of the best professors that I have had so far.
This prof peaked my interest in coastal management and made policy, planning and management - a dry topic, come to life.
What a nice young woman. She keeps her lecture slides "quick and dirty"!
